  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "We have to Upgrade the Davinci Developer Version to the 4.8 Version since the New Davinci  license is used"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "How to Upgrade Davinci Developer Tool For your Project"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "1.Install the Davinci Developer Tool with 4.8 version"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "https://bosch.sharepoint.com/:u:/r/sites/msteams_3178191/Shared%20Documents/General/DaVinci_Developer_4.8.30_SP1.zip?csf=1&web=1&e=Y6urMc"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "2.Update .dpa file"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Change the Davinci Developer install path"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Davinci%20Developer%20Upgrade/image2022-9-13_18-15-23.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Davinci Developer Upgrade/image2022-9-13_18-15-23.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "3.Update VIP_{Project}_DEV.bat"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Davinci%20Developer%20Upgrade/image2022-9-13_18-17-4.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Davinci Developer Upgrade/image2022-9-13_18-17-4.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "========================================================================================================"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Davinci Developer License in Wuxi Location"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "If you want to use  Davinci Developer License In Wuxi if have to install the Davinci Developer 4.10 from below Link"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "https://bosch.sharepoint.com/:u:/r/sites/msteams_3178191/Shared%20Documents/General/Vector%20Developer4.10.zip?csf=1&web=1&e=paUY08"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "You have to drag .dpa file with DevincI Developer 4.8 version to the Davinci Developer 4.10 Tool to open the developer Project"
    }
  ],
